    "canonical_note": "Traditionally within the Thondai Nadu grouping (approximately #34 range near Kanchipuram). Site places at #25 for organizational continuity within the Rama-avatar cluster arc (with #14 Kabisthalam, #18 Thiruvelliyangudi, #23 Thiruppullamboothankudi). Significant regional divergence from traditional Thondai Nadu placement.",
    "temple_name": "Sri Vijayaraghava Perumal Temple",
