    "canonical_note": "Traditionally canonical #41 per Sri Vaishnava sequence (verified via astroepanchang.com, templenet.com, aanmeegam.org). Site places at #28 for organizational continuity. One of the most famous Divya Desams — the Kallazhagar (Beautiful Stone Lord) shrine on Alagar Malai near Madurai, with 128 Alwar pasurams (among highest in the 108).",
