    "canonical_note": "Traditionally canonical #31 per Sri Vaishnava sequence. One of the most theologically foundational Nadu Nadu shrines — the birthplace of the three Mudhal Alwars (Poigai, Bhoothath, Peyalvar) who initiated the Alwar bhakti tradition. Site of the celebrated 'three Alwars in a well' narrative.",
