    "canonical_note": "Traditionally canonical position ~#105 per Sri Vaishnava sequence (Thiruvanvandoor). Site places at #95 for organizational continuity within Kerala Malai Nadu block. The 12th of the 13 Kerala Divya Desams — completing the Kerala pilgrimage circuit alongside Thiruvalla #96.",
